Package org.ironmaple.simulation.drivesims

Class SimplifiedSwerveDriveSimulation

java.lang.Object
edu.wpi.first.wpilibj2.command.SubsystemBase
org.ironmaple.simulation.drivesims.SimplifiedSwerveDriveSimulation
All Implemented Interfaces:
Sendable, Subsystem, AbstractSwerveDriveSubsystem
public class SimplifiedSwerveDriveSimulation extends SubsystemBase implements AbstractSwerveDriveSubsystem

An easier way to simulate swerve drive.

This class serves as the drive subsystem code during simulation.

It controls a SwerveDriveSimulation, just like how your swerve subsystem code controls the real drivetrain.
